hopobject.body: Would you like to leave a message? windpharmacy.biz FYI, people were alble to buy private health insurance before the ACA. The reason they didn't was because they didn't have the money or wish to spend the money on insurance. Why would they when they could just go to the emergency room and get free health care. The best way to change the health care system would be for all citizens to drop their health care insurance.
